                         shows the most frequent combinations of partners in CSSPs by subsector, displayed as a network graph. While the size of the nodes corresponds to the absolute number of actors from the respective subsector (see Table 3), the thickness of the edges relates to the number of CSSPs involving at least one actor from both connected subsectors (see Table 4
